trans-unit.source: This class converts a parameter in a query string to an object of the appropriate type.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen konverterer en parameter i en spørringsstreng til et objekt av riktig type.

trans-unit.source: It can also convert a parameter from an object to its query string representation.
trans-unit.target: Det kan også konvertere parameteren fra et objekt til strengrepresentasjon den spørringen.

trans-unit.source: Parameters can be specified in a query string within a URL.
trans-unit.target: Parametere kan angis i en spørringsstreng i en URL-adresse.

trans-unit.source: This class takes those parameters specified in a string and converts them into objects.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen tar disse parameterne som er angitt i en streng, og konverteres til objekter.

trans-unit.source: For example, the following contract is defined.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel er følgende kontrakten definert.

trans-unit.source: ``` [ServiceContract] interface Calculator { [WebGet(UriTemplate="Add?n1={n1}&n2={n2}")] [OperationContract] long Add(long n1, long n2); } ``` A [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] service implements this interface and exposes it on an endpoint with the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WebHttpBehavior> at http://localhost:8000/MyCalcService.
trans-unit.target: ``` [ServiceContract] interface Calculator { [WebGet(UriTemplate="Add?n1={n1}&n2={n2}")] [OperationContract] long Add(long n1, long n2); } ```En [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] tjenesten implementerer dette grensesnittet og viser på et sluttpunkt med de <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WebHttpBehavior>på http://localhost:8000/MyCalcService.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WebHttpBehavior>

trans-unit.source: The `Add` service operation can be called by sending an HTTP GET to http://localhost:8000/MyCalcService/Add?n1=10&n2=5.
trans-unit.target: Den `Add` tjenesteoperasjon kan kalles ved å sende en HTTP-GET http://localhost:8000/MyCalcService/Legg? n1 =&10; n2 =&5;.

trans-unit.source: The QueryStringConverter receives this URL and converts the two parameters (n1 and n2) specified in the URL into two `long` objects with the appropriate values.
trans-unit.target: QueryStringConverter mottar denne URL-adressen og konverterer de to parameterne (n1 og n2) som angitt i URL-adressen i to `long` objekter med de nødvendige verdiene.

trans-unit.source: You can derive a class from QueryStringConverter to control how query string parameters are mapped into a service operation's parameters.
trans-unit.target: Du kan utledet en klasse fra QueryStringConverter å styre hvordan spørringsparametere streng er tilordnet til en tjenesteoperasjon parametere.

trans-unit.source: The QueryStringConverter supports the following types by default: - <xref:System.Byte> - <xref:System.SByte> - <xref:System.Int16> - <xref:System.Int32> - <xref:System.Int64> - <xref:System.UInt16> - <xref:System.UInt32> - <xref:System.UInt64> - <xref:System.Single> - <xref:System.Double> - <xref:System.Char> - <xref:System.Decimal> - <xref:System.Boolean> - <xref:System.String> - <xref:System.DateTime> - <xref:System.TimeSpan> - <xref:System.Guid> - <xref:System.Byte> array - <xref:System.Uri> - <xref:System.Object> - <xref:System.DateTimeOffset> - Enums - Types that have a `TypeConverterAttribute` that can convert the type to and from a string representation.
trans-unit.target: QueryStringConverter støtter følgende typer som standard:- <xref:System.Byte>- <xref:System.SByte>- <xref:System.Int16>- <xref:System.Int32>- <xref:System.Int64>- <xref:System.UInt16>- <xref:System.UInt32>- <xref:System.UInt64>- <xref:System.Single>- <xref:System.Double>- <xref:System.Char>- <xref:System.Decimal>- <xref:System.Boolean>- <xref:System.String>- <xref:System.DateTime>- <xref:System.TimeSpan>- <xref:System.Guid>- <xref:System.Byte>matrise - <xref:System.Uri>- <xref:System.Object>- <xref:System.DateTimeOffset>- opplistinger - typer som har en `TypeConverterAttribute` som kan konvertere typen til og fra en strengrepresentasjon.</xref:System.DateTimeOffset> </xref:System.Object> </xref:System.Uri> </xref:System.Byte> </xref:System.Guid> </xref:System.TimeSpan> </xref:System.DateTime> </xref:System.String> </xref:System.Boolean> </xref:System.Decimal> </xref:System.Char> </xref:System.Double> </xref:System.Single> </xref:System.UInt64> </xref:System.UInt32> </xref:System.UInt16> </xref:System.Int64> </xref:System.Int32> </xref:System.Int16> </xref:System.SByte> </xref:System.Byte>

trans-unit.source: Determines whether the specified type can be converted to and from a string representation.
trans-unit.target: Bestemmer om den angitte typen kan konverteres til og fra en strengrepresentasjon.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Type> to convert.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Type>til å konvertere.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: A value that specifies whether the type can be converted.
trans-unit.target: En verdi som angir om typen kan konverteres.

trans-unit.source: Converts a query string parameter to the specified type.
trans-unit.target: Konverterer en streng spørringsparameter til den angitte typen.

trans-unit.source: If the `parameterType` is a value type and the parameter is `null`, then the default value of the `parameterType` is returned.
trans-unit.target: Hvis den `parameterType` er en verditype og parameteren `null`, deretter standardverdien for den `parameterType` returneres.

trans-unit.source: The string form of the parameter and value.
trans-unit.target: Streng formatet parameteren og -verdien.

trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Type>ikke konvertere parameteren til å.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.target: Konvertere parameter.
